Package: fractalplotr
Type: Package
Title: Plot Beautiful Fractals with R
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: person("Sebastian", "Henz", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  email = "bastihz.dev@posteo.de")
Maintainer: Sebastian Henz <bastihz.dev@posteo.de>
Description: Plot beautiful fractals in R. This package lets you crate fractals 
    of various types, for example Mandelbrot sets, Julia sets or dragon curves. 
    It provides functions for plotting them with many colorful defaults. You 
    can easily customize the plots with your own color palettes and even create 
    zoomed-in plots of some fractals.
